page.title: 05The Industrial estate.
page.content: This land space is covered with 49% Industrial 49% housing, and 2% shops.This area has two snack bars with 18 garages with servicing, one garden centre one church, two metal manufactures, two brick or cement works one pub. As garages with servicing is seen the most,this means that it is a high car ownership area.This is one of the most densely populated areas on the outskirts of a major housing estate. The industrial area is broken down into small sections,they cover a wide variety; from concrete works to scrap yards, form worldwide distributors to small scale plastic moulding works. This provides work for a large section 0f the community.
